OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FRachel Reeves is set to meet her US
OL,8,Fcounterpart after he said "a small bit
OL,9,Fof economic pain" caused by the Iran
OL,10,Fwar was worth it to prevent Tehran
OL,11,Fgetting a nuclear weapon.
OL,13,FThe comments by US treasury secretary
OL,14,FScott Bessent put him at odds with the
OL,15,FChancellor, who has gone public with
OL,16,Fher anger and frustration at the
OL,17,F"folly" of America's actions in the
OL,18,FMiddle East and its financial fallout
OL,19,Fon families.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@QO]yD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThe pair were due to hold face-to-face
OL,8,Ftalks in Washington DC on Wednesday
OL,9,Fduring the spring meetings of the
OL,10,FInternational Monetary Fund, which
OL,11,Fwill be dominated by the ongoing
OL,12,Fcrisis in the Gulf, which has
OL,13,Finflicted a global economic shock and
OL,14,Fsent energy prices soaring.
OL,16,FPrior to the Chancellor heading
OL,17,Fstateside, the influential financial
OL,18,Fbody slashed Britain's economic growth
OL,19,Fforecast as a result of the conflict
OL,20,Fand warned a worldwide recession could
OL,21,Fbe a "close call" in a severe scenario.
OL,26,@}D@FOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FHowever, despite the "large" jolt to
OL,8,Fthe global economy, Bank of England
OL,9,Fgovernor Andrew Bailey said the UK was
OL,10,Fmuch better placed to deal with it
OL,11,Fbecause of its resilient banking
OL,12,Fsystem, forged in the wake of the 2007-
OL,13,F09 financial crisis.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, President Donald Trump has
OL,16,Fsaid a second round of talks between
OL,17,Fthe US and Iran could happen "over the
OL,18,Fnext two days", after negotiations at
OL,19,Fthe weekend collapsed.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@\O]yD@^OUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FTehran's nuclear ambitions were a key
OL,8,Fsticking point.
OL,10,FDiplomats have been working behind the
OL,11,Fscenes as the US imposed its blockade
OL,12,Fof Iranian ports and Tehran threatened
OL,13,Fretaliatory strikes across the region,
OL,14,Famid a shaky ceasefire.
OL,16,FAt the same time Prime Minister Sir
OL,17,FKeir Starmer is seeking to co-ordinate
OL,18,Finternational efforts to ensure the
OL,19,Fstrategic Strait of Hormuz can remain
OL,20,Fopen to shipping after hostilities end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThe critical waterway, used to move
OL,8,Fone fifth of the world's oil and gas
OL,9,Fsupplies, has become a major
OL,10,Fflashpoint in the conflict, with its
OL,11,Feffective closure by Iran hiking the
OL,12,Fcost of fuel, food and other basic
OL,13,Fgoods.
OL,15,FHowever, responding to the spike in
OL,16,Fprices, Mr Bessent said "a small bit
OL,17,Fof economic pain for a few weeks is
OL,18,Fworth taking off the incalculable tail
OL,19,Frisk of either a nuclear Iran or a
OL,20,Fnuclear Iran that uses that weapon".
OL,26,@xD@YOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FHe insisted "there is nothing more
OL,8,Ftransient than what we are seeing
OL,9,Fnow", and added: "So the conflict will
OL,10,Fend, prices will come down, and then
OL,11,Fheadline inflation will come down, and
OL,12,Fwith that, gasoline prices will come
OL,13,Fdown."
OL,15,FMr Bessent made his remarks after Ms
OL,16,FReeves told the Mirror newspaper: "I
OL,17,Ffeel very frustrated and angry that
OL,18,Fthe US went into this war without a
OL,19,Fclear exit plan, without a clear idea
OL,20,Fof what they were trying to achieve."
OL,26,@oD@MOUqD@DO]qD@ROUuD@FO]xD@cOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
