FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FShe branded it a "folly" that impacted
OL,8,Fhouseholds in the UK and around the
OL,9,Fworld.
OL,11,FMr Trump has defended the blockade
OL,12,Faimed at putting pressure on Iran,
OL,13,Farguing its control of the strait
OL,14,Famounted to blackmail and extortion.
OL,16,FHe has warned that any hostile Iranian
OL,17,Fboats approaching American warships
OL,18,Fwould be "immediately eliminated".
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@XO]zD@JOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
