PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776228833
OL,3,CChancellor to hold talks with US
OL,4,Ccounterpart after strong criticism of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FUS Central Command, which directs
OL,8,Fmilitary operations in the Middle
OL,9,FEast, said no vessels have so far run
OL,10,Fthe blockade.
OL,12,FAmong those ships being barred include
OL,13,FChinese tankers.
OL,15,FIn response, the country's president
OL,16,FXi Jinping said nations should "oppose
OL,17,Fthe world's retrogression to the law
OL,18,Fof the jungle".
OL,26,@xD@`OUzD@NO]
